i": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA LAW WA JADTO SHAFEE-A’N AQRABA ILAIKA MIM MOHAMMADIW WA AHLE-BAIYTE-HIL AKHYAA-RIL ATQEYAAA-IL ABRAA-RE A’LAI-HE WA A’LAI-HE-MUS SALAAMO LAS TASHFA’TO BE-HIM ILAIKA WA HAAZAA QABRO WALIY-YIM MIN AWLIYAAA-E-KA WA SAYYE-DIM MIN ASFEYAAA-E-KA WA MAN FARAZ-TA A’LAL KHALQE TAA-A’TA-HU.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ لَوْ وَجَدْتُ شَفِيْعًا اَقْرَبَ اِلَيْكَ مِنْ مُّحَمَّدٍ وَّاَهْلِ بَيْتِهِ الْاَخْيَارِ الْاَتْقِيَآءِ الْاَبْرَارِ عَلَيْهِ وَعَلَيْهِمُ السَّلَامُ لَا سْتَشْفَعْتُ بِهِمْ اِلَيْكَ وَهٰذَا قَبْرُ وَلِيٍّ مِّنْ اَوْلِيَآئِكَ‏ وَسَيِّدٍ مِّنْ اَصْفِيَآئِكَ وَمَنْ فَرَضْتَ عَلَى الْخَلْقِ طَاعَتَهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGree