English": "O Allah! Surely, I do not rely on my past virtuous actions, and I do not rely upon good actions performed with evidence from me, but if I come with all the good deeds of Your creatures then disobey the order of Your guardian, these good deeds will keep me away from Your vicinity, not coming as a barrier between me and Your fire. Then for this I know that the best obedience is the obedience of Your guardian.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNEE LAA O-A’WWELO A’LAA SAALE-HATIN SALA-FAT MINNEE WA LAA A-SEKO BE-HASANA-TIN TAQOO-MO BIL-HUJJATE ANNEE WA LAW ANNEE QADDAM-TO HASANAA-TE JAMEE-E’ KHALQE-KA SUMMA KHAALAF-TO TAA-A’TA AWLEYAAA-E-KA LA-KAA-NAT TILKAL HASANAATO MAZ-E’JATAL LEE A’N JAWAARE-KA GHAIRA HAA-E-LA-TAM BAIYNEE WA BAIYNA NAARE-KA FALE-ZAALE-KA A’LIMTO ANNA AFZALA TAA-A’TEKA TAA-A’TO AWLIYAAA-E-KA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ لَا اُعَوِّلُ عَلٰى صَالِحَةٍ سَلَفَتْ مِنِّيْ وَلَا اَثِقُ بِحَسَنَةٍ تَقُوْمُ بِالْحُجَّةِ عَنِّيْ وَلَوْ اَنِّيْ قَدَّمْتُ حَسَنَاتِ جَمِيْعِ خَلْقِكَ ثُمَّ خَالَفْتُ طَاعَةَ اَوْلِيَآئِكَ لَكَانَتْ تِلْكَ الْـحَسَنَاتُ مُزْعِـجَةً لِّيْ عَنْ جِوَارِكَ غَيْرَ حَآئِلَةٍۢ بَيْنِيْ وَبَيْنَ نَارِكَ فَلِذٰلِكَ عَلِمْتُ اَنَّ اَفْضَلَ طَاعَتِكَ طَاعَةُ اَوْلِيَآئِكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014648, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! Have mercy on my approach by what I have turned to You, then surely You know that I cannot find anybody greater than You, for the place he has in front of You, O Most Merciful of all! O Allah! Surely You are described with the bestowing and Your vicegerent with intercession towards the one who is known, then intercede for me with grace, as Your face (of mercy) is approaching me, and if Your face is approaching me than Paradise will be my residence.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUM-MAR HAM TAWAJJO-HEE BE-MAN TAWAJJAH-TO BEHEE ILAIKA FALA-QAD A’LIMTA ANNEE GHAIRO WAAJE-DIN A’ZAMO MIQDAA-RAM MIN-HUM LE-MAKAANE-HIM MINKA YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEEN. ALLAAHUMMA INNAKA BIL-IN-AA’ME MAWSOO-FOON WA WALIYYO-KA BISH-SHAFAA-A’TE LE-MAN ATAA-HO MA’ROO-FOON FA-IZAA SHAFA-A’ FEEYA MOTA-FAZZE-LAN KAANA WAJHO-KA A’LAIYYA MUQBE-LAN WA IZAA KAANA WAJHO-KA A’LAIYYA MUQBE-LAN A-SAB-TO MINAL JANNATE MANZE-LAN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ ارْحَمْ تَوَجُّهِيْ بِمَنْ تَوَجَّهْتُ بِهٖ اِلَيْكَ فَلَقَدْ عَلِمْتَ اَنِّيْ غَيْرُ وَاجِدٍ اَعْظَمُ مِقْدَارًا مِّنْهُمْ لِمَكَانِهِمْ مِنْكَ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّكَ بِالْاِنْعَامِ مَوْصُوْفٌ وَ وَلِيُّكَ بِالشَّفَاعَةِ لِمَنْ اَتَاهُ مَعْرُوْفٌ فَاِذَا شَفَعَ فِيَّ مُتَفَضِّلًا كَانَ وَجْهُكَ عَلَيَّ مُقْبِلًا وَاِذَا كَانَ وَجْهُكَ عَلَيَّ مُقْبِلًا اَصَبْتُ مِنَ الْجَنَّةِ مَنْزِلًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014649, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! Then I seek intercession with You that bestow upon me with pleasure and bounty. O Allah! Make him happy from us, and do not enrage on us, and guide us to him and do not deviate in it, and make for us in it a way which he has chosen, and increase my obedience till (it reach) pure intention in my greetings, O Most Merciful of all!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA FA-KAMAA ATA-WASSALO BEHEE ILAIKA AN TAMUNNA A’LAIYYA BIR-REZAA WAN-NE-A’AME. ALLAAHUMMA ARZE-HI ANNAA WA LAA TUS-KHIT-HO A’LAI-NAA WAHDE-NAA BEHEE WA LAA TOZIL-LANAA FEEHE WAJ-A’LNAA FEEHE A’LASSA-BEE-LIL LAZEE TAKH-TAARO-HU WA AZIF TAA-A’TEE ILAA KHAALE-SE NIYYATEE FEE TA-HIYYA-TEE YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ فَكَمَا اَتَوَسَّلُ بِهٖ اِلَيْكَ اَنْ تَمُنَّ عَلَيَّ بِالرِّضَا وَالنِّعَمِ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اَرْضِهٖ عَنَّا وَلَا تُسْخِطْهُ عَلَيْنَا وَاهْدِنَا بِهٖ وَلَا تُضِلَّنَا فِيْهِ وَاجْعَلْنَا فِيْهِ عَلَى السَّبِيْلِ الَّذِيْ تَخْتَارُهٗ وَاَضِفْ طَاعَتِيْ اِلٰى خَالِصِ نِيَّتِيْ فِيْ تَحِيَّتِيْ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014650, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! Send blessings upon the best of Your creature, Muhammad and his progeny, like You have selected them upon the worlds, and chosen them from the past (generation). O Allah! And send blessings upon Your vicegerent, and Your chosen one from Your creatures, subsequently on Your Prophet, endurer for Your command, Ali Ibn Abi Taalib and send blessings upon Fatema Zahra, the mistress of the women of the worlds, and send blessings upon al-Hasan and al-Husain, the two earings of Your throne, and Your two proofs for Your creatures upon You, and callers towards You.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA KHEYAARE KHALQE-KA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE-HI KAMAN TA-JABTA-HUM A’LAL A’ALAMEENA WAKH-TARTA-HUM A’LAA I’L-MIN MINAL AWWALEENA. ALLAAHUMMA WA-SALLE A’LAA HUJJATE-KA WA SAFWATE-KA MIN BARIY-YATE-KA ATTAA-LEE LE-NABIYYE-KAL MOQEE-ME LE-AMRE-KA A’LIYYIB-NE ABEE TAALE-BIN WA SALLE A’LAA FAATEMA-TAZ ZAHRAAA-E SAYYADA-TE NESAAA-IL A’A-LAMEENA WA SALLE A’LAL HASANE WAL HUSAINE SHANA-FAIY A’R-SHE-KA WA DALEE-LEE KHALQE-KA A’LAIKA WA DO-A’ATE-HIM ILAIKA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى خِيَارِ خَلْقِكَ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِهٖ كَمَا انْتَجَبْتَ